\end{itemize}
After the architectural JSON schema is extracted, three parallel execution routes securely synchronize. The Scikit-Learn Predictive Regressor\cite{sklearn2024, breiman2001} instantly evaluates physical square footage and perimeter mapping to output highly-local expense predictions\cite{wang2020}. Simultaneously, the Groq Advanced LLM\cite{groq2024, brown2020} interprets incoming room parameters to structure a spatial response logic mapping. Ultimately, the finalized 
